<p itemprop="description">A senior service owner leads complex, high-impact services and provides expert guidance on service strategy and delivery. They mentor service owners and work with senior stakeholders to drive service transformation and innovation.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead strategic service transformation and innovation initiatives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Develop service strategy aligned with organisational objectives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Mentor service owners and establish service best practices</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Work with senior leadership on strategic service decisions</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Drive continuous improvement in service delivery practices</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Manage complex stakeholder relationships and service dependencies</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Influence policy and strategic direction through service insights</li>
    </ul>
</section>

